								                Only a small amount of work is required on the Government installation (<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">e.g.,</i>a few brief visits permonth); or</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1849e42" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
